       <p>A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart.

       I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so.</p>
       
       <h3><a href="">someone else</a></h3>
       <p>O my friend -- but it is too much for my strength -- I sink under the weight of the splendour of these visions! A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart.</p>

