       <p>O my friend -- but it is too much for my strength -- I sink under the weight of the splendour of these visions! A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart.</p>     
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-2"></div>
      <div class="col-md-8">

    


        <form id="postNewComment" class="form-horizontal" method="post" action="/items/comment" enctype='multipart/form-data'>

            <div class="form-group form-group-lg">
              <div class="col-sm-12">
                <textarea rows="4" name="text" class="form-control" maxlength="300" required ></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group form-group-lg">
              <div class="col-sm-12">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">POST A COMMENT</button>
              </div>
            </div>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-2"></div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-2"></div>
</div>
